{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setDragState:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNAnnotationViewDragState","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationViewDragState","preciseIdentifier":"c:@E@MLNAnnotationViewDragState"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dragState","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can override this method to animate a custom annotation view as the user","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"drags it. As the system detects user actions that would indicate a drag, it","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"calls this method to update the drag state.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the current drag state for the annotation view."}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setDragState:animated:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setDragState:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L279"},"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setDragState:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(im)setDragState:animated:","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"setDragState:animated:","roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setdragstate:animated:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","title":"MLNAnnotationView","role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference"},{"text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object that corresponds to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/setDragState:animated:":{"title":"setDragState:animated:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setDragState:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setDragState:animated:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setdragstate:animated:","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setDragState:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the current drag state for the annotation view."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationViewDragState":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotationViewDragState","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationviewdragstate","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationViewDragState"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"These constants indicate the current drag state of an annotation view."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationViewDragState"}}}